        <item>
            <title>Nikon Z50II 登场，EXPEED 7 影像处理引擎  + 1 秒「释放前拍摄」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/08/nikon-z50ii/dc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=nikon-z50ii</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/08/nikon-z50ii/dc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 15:00:11 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[数码相机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[EXPEED 7]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[nikon]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Nikon Z50II]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Nikon Z9]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1273985</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Nikon 最新推出 Z50II，别因为它机仔细细，使用 APS-C （DX）格式而小看它，其采用与旗舰型号 Z9 相同的 EXPEED 7 影像处理引擎，并加入了不少方便创作的功能，例如增强了对焦准确度和追焦能力量，同时加入全新「Picture Control」按键，方便用家快速转换不同颜色设定。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273991" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_40_2_front34l-687x580.jpg" alt="" width="687" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_40_2_front34l-687x580.jpg 687w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_40_2_front34l-1066x900.jpg 1066w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_40_2_front34l-scaled.jpg 1067w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 687px" /></p><p>Nikon Z50II 创新增设「成像配方」（Imaging Recipe）功能，提供色彩、亮度、对比度等多重个人化选择，让用户轻松切换风格。此外，相机设有全新 Picture Control 按键，用户可即时启用多种预设色彩设定，无论使用自动模式或手动模式，均可简单变换滤镜效果，拍摄更具灵活性。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273990" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_01_jn_1889_z_d-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_01_jn_1889_z_d-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_01_jn_1889_z_d-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲成像配方 – Nights like this © Dondre Green</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273989" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_01_dg_5131_z_d-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_01_dg_5131_z_d-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_01_dg_5131_z_d-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲成像配方 – 成像配方 – Summertime Cool © Julie Nimke</p><p>Z50II 采用与旗舰型号 Z9 相同的 EXPEED 7 影像处理引擎，支援 Z9 所设的「9 种主体侦测模式」，能自动识别并聚焦动态主体，自动设定 AF 模式，拍摄时即使目标动作多变，也能保持精准对焦。此引擎搭配深度学习技术，能即时分析场景，并自动调整曝光、快门速度和感光度等拍摄设定，用家只需按下快门，便能轻松获得优质影像。配备「释放前拍摄」功能，更可在完全按下快门释放按键前拍摄影像，缓冲时间长达一秒，不怕错失重要画面。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273993" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241108161553-694x464.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="464" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241108161553-694x464.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241108161553.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Z50II 进一步提升影片拍摄性能，具备 5.6K 超取样功能，可创作高解析度 4K UHD 影片，并支援 N-Log 格式，赋予影片更丰富的色调层次。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273987" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_04_jn_2732_z_d-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_04_jn_2732_z_d-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_04_jn_2732_z_d-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273988" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_00_dg_0877_ps-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_00_dg_0877_ps-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/z50ii_00_dg_0877_ps-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>此外，Z50II 加入影片自拍功能，用家在按下录影键后，能设定 2 秒或 10 秒延迟开始录影，便于后期编辑处理。Z50II 亦是 Nikon 首部加入产品评价模式的 Z 系相机，相机将会对焦前景物件。除此之外更支援 USB 串流传输，只需将相机连接至电脑或手机，即可在网上会议或直播中使用高画质影像。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273994" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241108161759-694x465.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="465" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241108161759-694x465.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241108161759.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可使用 USB 串流直播</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273995" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241108161942-694x465.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="465" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241108161942-694x465.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241108161942.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲「产品评价模式」下相机将会对焦前景物件</p><p>Z50II 配备亮度达 1000 cd/m² 的电子观景器，比 Z50 提升近一倍，无论在户外或室内，用户都能轻松观察构图及影像细节，减轻眼部疲劳。通过高亮度 EVF，拍摄时能更专注于主体，轻松掌控影像效果，提升拍摄乐趣。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273996" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241108162128-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241108162128-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/20241108162128.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Z50II 同步推出的 MC-DC3 遥控线，适合夜间拍摄及长时间曝光情境，有效减少相机震动，保持稳定成像。用家可远距释放快门，连续拍摄或进行长曝，适合拍摄星空或静态场景。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1273997" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/27241mcdc3remoteh7az-682x580.png" alt="" width="682" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/27241mcdc3remoteh7az-682x580.png 682w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/27241mcdc3remoteh7az.png 700w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 682px" /></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/11/08/nikon-z50ii/dc/">Nikon Z50II 登场，EXPEED 7 影像处理引擎  + 1 秒「释放前拍摄」</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
