        <item>
            <title>【评测】MacBook Pro M4 2024  详细效能评测 + 选购指南分析 7 大要点</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/08/macbook-pro-m4-2024-review/notebook/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=macbook-pro-m4-2024-review</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/08/macbook-pro-m4-2024-review/notebook/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 14:00:34 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流动电脑]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[评测]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[macbook]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[macbook pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MacBook Pro 2024]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MacBook Pro M4]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电脑]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1274013</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 最新推出 M4 MacBook Pro 系列，再度在设计、效能以及智能功能上推陈出新。这次升级进一步提升硬件效能，令处理影片剪辑等多媒体创作者注入新动力之外，还于机身设计上进行微调，并引入 Apple Intelligence 的 AI 智能功能，大幅提高用户工作效率。M4 版 MacBook Pro 展现出高效能、电池耐用、配套丰富、使用便利等，大家对高效笔电的极致追求。以下小编会就 MacBook Pro 软硬件各方面进行评测，看看你在选购时，选择贴合自己需要的型号、选配选项。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274095 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03686-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03686-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03686.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>选购要点 <b>1. </b>设计细节</h2><p>新款 MacBook Pro 的外型在上代基础上进行了微调，利用特别电镀技术制作「太空黑」配色，给人低调而奢华的机身设计。MagSafe 充电线与太空黑机身也有特别搭配，相比起 MacBook Air 的午夜黑，更加增强了黑色视觉效果。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03707.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274061" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03707-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03707-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03707.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03709.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274062" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03709-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03709-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03709.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03698.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274058" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03698-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03698-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03698.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03701.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274059" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03701-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03701-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03701.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03703.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274060" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03703-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03703-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03703.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03714.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274063" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03714-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03714-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03714.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03713.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274064" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03713-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03713-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03713.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>MacBook Pro 太空黑在充电线上也改良到更加「黑」，颜色上配套做得更好。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03725-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274102" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03725-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03725-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03725-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03724-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274103" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03724-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03724-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03724-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲左手边是午夜黑的充电线，右手边是 MacBook Pro 太空黑所附属的充电线</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03726-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274105" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03726-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03726-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03726-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲左方是今次介绍的太空黑 MacBook Pro M4 版本，右手边的是午夜黑 MacBook Air。可见两者色系有分别</p><h2>选购要点 <b>2. 1000nits </b>高亮度荧幕与 <b>Nano Texture </b>抗反光纳米纹理显示器</h2><p>新款 MacBook Pro 用家可选择加钱配置具抗反光功能的 Nano Texture 纳米纹理显示器，提升在复杂灯光环境，或者强光环境下的显示效果。例如在咖啡室，室内可能有好多零散灯光，一个个灯泡显示在你的画面上，你甚至可在画面看到自己的样貌。Nano Texture 纳米纹理显示器就可大幅减低这些反射现象。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274096 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03722-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03722-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03722.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/vlcsnap2024110817h22.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274047" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/vlcsnap2024110817h22-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/vlcsnap2024110817h22-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/vlcsnap2024110817h22.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024110882813-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1274044 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024110882813-694x283.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="283" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024110882813-694x283.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2024110882813-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>但你也要留意，就同手机的抗反射芒贴一样，即使 Apple 已做得很好，但仍然有光亮度低减、对比度与黑位深度有轻微下跌的现象，不一定适合对画面效果有极度要求，例如图像处理的用家。建议使用者根据需求选择。之不过这部 M4 MacBook Pro 带来了全新 Liquid Retina XDR 显示器，观看一般内容时可提供达 1000nits 光亮度，而在显示 HDR 内容时光亮度更可达 1600nits，它可以抵销到 Nano Texture 纳米纹理显示器对光线透通度的影响，除非你经常需要把荧幕亮度开到最大，否则光度低减的问题可以忽视。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03717.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274050" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03717-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03717-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03717.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03719.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1274048" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03719-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03719-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc03719.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
